Type: Package
Package: mfsusieR
Title: Multi-Modality Sum of Single Functions Regression
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2026-04-25
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gao", "Wang", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "wang.gao@columbia.edu"),
    person("William R. P.", "Denault", role = "aut"),
    person("Anjing", "Liu", role = "aut"),
    person("Matthew", "Stephens", role = "aut"))
Description: A multi-modality generalisation of the 'Sum of Single
    Functions' (SuSiF) model for variable selection in regression
    with mixtures of functional and scalar responses. Built on the
    'susieR' backbone, with wavelet-based functional priors and a
    per-(scale, modality) variance structure.
